data.description: Show Stopper!! Situated on a nice .41 acre lot in the highly desired Oxton Subdivision you will find this well kept home that was built in 2014. Featuring 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, an oversized heated and cooled finished bonus room upstairs (NEW HVAC Installed 2023); which could be a 4th bedroom, 2 car attached garage, in ground sprinkler system, and  nice big backyard. Step inside to find a modern home that includes; hardwood and tile flooring, detailed trim work, custom cabinetry with granite counter tops throughout whole home, stainless steel appliances (New Bosch Dishwasher 2023), a gas fireplace, built in surround sound in living room and neutral colors throughout. Enjoy the outdoors? No Problem!! In the back there is a beautiful 16X32 Gunite pool for those hot Georgia summer days and a Bullfrog spa for those cold fall/winter night's. Surround sound system installed outside for entertainment. Back yard is fully fenced in with plenty of room for children or fur animals to play. But wait, there is more!! On property is a 16X22 roll-up shop for those who need extra storage or a working area. There truly is something for everyone here. You don't want to miss this one!  COUNTY TAXES ONLY!! NO HOA!! Houston County Schools! 15 Min to RAFB, 5 min to BUCEES, and centrally located to all shopping.
